About the event Yoga and Meditation with Pamela Rose

Yoga & Meditation with Pamela Rose Wednesday, August 21st 6-7PM BRING YOUR OWN YOGA MAT $20 Drop in Cost

Join us for a blissful Yoga & Meditation Night at Blumen Gardens on Wednesday, August 21st, from 6-7pm! Immerse yourself in an all-levels class focusing on breath and body connection.

Experience the transformative power of somatic healing techniques, yin yoga, introspective sensory meditation, body shaking, and tapping. Settle into the parasympathetic nervous system, creating a safe space for emotional expression, healing, and deep relaxation.
